Global Electrical Sheet Molding Compound (SMC) Market Insights
Electrical Sheet Molding Compound (SMC) Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.00 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Electrical Sheet Molding Compound (SMC) Market Overview
The Electrical Sheet Molding Compound (SMC) market is poised to witness significant growth due to the increasing demand for lightweight, high-performance materials in the electrical and automotive sectors. The market is estimated to reach a value of USD 4.5 billion by 2027, driven by innovations in material science and the need for efficient, durable components in electrical applications. The SMC technology is widely used in electrical enclosures, transformers, and other components that require robust electrical insulation and mechanical properties. The growing trend toward electric vehicles (EVs) and renewable energy solutions is also expected to contribute to the expansion of this market.

